Tiers exclus              $$\frac{}{\Gamma\vdash\phi\vee\neg\phi}T$$

Preuve par l'absurde      $$\frac{\Gamma,\phi\vdash\psi\wedge\neg\psi}
                            {\Gamma\vdash\neg\phi}A$$

Introduction du *et*      $$\frac{\Gamma\vdash\phi \qquad
                            \Gamma\vdash\psi}{\Gamma\vdash\phi\wedge\psi}I_\wedge$$

Élimination du *et*       $$\frac{\Gamma\vdash\phi\wedge\psi}{\Gamma\vdash\phi}L_\wedge$$

                          $$\frac{\Gamma\vdash\phi\wedge\psi}{\Gamma\vdash\psi}R_\wedge$$

Introduction du *ou*      $$\frac{\Gamma\vdash\phi}{\Gamma\vdash\phi\vee\psi}L_\vee$$

                          $$\frac{\Gamma\vdash\psi}{\Gamma\vdash\phi\vee\psi}R_\vee$$

Élimination du *ou*       $$\frac{\Gamma\vdash\phi\vee\psi \qquad \Gamma\vdash\phi\to\chi
